If you are reading this review , chancs are that you aleady know who Raymond Scott is . ||| 1
This is the CD that started the revival of interest in his music . ||| 1
Raymond and his original group are the real masters of his music although the Beau Hunks are a very close second . ||| 1
Raymond left no room for error on his recordings and it shows . ||| 1
The performances are completely polished . ||| 1
True these all come from 78 RPM sources but they are as good as it gets . ||| 1
You will NOT be disappointed . ||| 1
If you only buy one Raymond Scott CD , this MUST be the one to get . ||| 1
